#: src/introduction.md:1
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "介紹"

#: src/introduction.md:5
msgid ""
"This is the **Redox OS** book, which will go through (almost) everything "
"about Redox: design, philosophy, how it works, how you can contribute, how "
"to deploy Redox, and much more."
msgstr ""
"這是 **Redox OS** 的手冊，將涵蓋（幾乎）所有有關 Redox 的內容：設計、理念、如"
"何運作、如何貢獻、如何部署 Redox，以及更多其他內容。"

#: src/introduction.md:7
msgid ""
"**Please keep in mind that this book is work-in-progress and sometimes can "
"be outdated, any help to improve it is important.**"
msgstr ""

